@startuml
title CI Test Import Graph (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFDF7
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Courier

actor "GitHub Actions\n(npm test)" as gha #E6F3FF
rectangle "Repo Root\nnode_modules" as rootMods #FFE6E6
rectangle "Root Test\nreact-test-sdk-hooks-integration.test.ts" as rootTest #FFF2CC
rectangle "Test SDK Server\ntest-sdk/src/server.ts" as sdkServer #F4E1FF
component "express package" as expressPkg #FFD6D6

gha --> rootTest : run Node test runner
rootTest --> sdkServer : import createAthenaTestSdkServer()
sdkServer --> expressPkg : import express
expressPkg -[dashed]-> rootMods : resolve from root install

note right of rootMods
Root package.json has no express in devDependencies.
CI clean install does not provide express in root node_modules.
end note

note bottom of expressPkg #FFCDD2
ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND in CI
Cannot find package 'express'
end note
@enduml
